### Payment API
@host = http://localhost:3001
@token = REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Plan-н QPay invoice үүсгэх
POST {{host}}/api/payment/invoice
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planType": "COMBO",
  "period": "monthly"
}

### Нэг видеог 72 цагаар түрээслэх invoice
POST {{host}}/api/payment/vod-invoice
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vodId": "youtubeId_or_dbId",
  "price": 2900,
  "title": "Test video"
}

### Төлбөр шалгах
POST {{host}}/api/payment/check
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceId": "clx_test"
}

### Invoice цуцлах
DELETE {{host}}/api/payment/invoice/clx_test
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Худалдан авалтын түүх
GET {{host}}/api/payment/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
